.PP
wxWidgets docs: wxChildFocusEvent

.SS "Events"

.PP
Use \fIwxEvtHandler:connect/3\fR with \fIwxChildFocusEventType\fR to subscribe to events of this type.

.SH DATA TYPES
.LP
.B
